        public List<String> getObjectPids(int offset,
                         int pageSize)
        Gets a page of object pids that exist in the repository. The current implementation relies on the following ITQL query against the resource index to fetch results. 
          select     $object
    from       <#ri>
    where      $object <info:fedora/fedora-system:def/model#hasModel>
        <info:fedora/fedora-system:FedoraObject-3.0>
    order by   $object
    limit      -pageSize-
    offset     -offset-

      • getSize

        public long getSize()
        Gets the size (total number of objects) of the underlying fedora 3 repository. The current implementation relies on the following ITQL query against the resource index to determine repository size. 
          select count(
        select     $object
        from       <#ri>
        where      $object <info:fedora/fedora-system:def/model#hasModel>
            <info:fedora/fedora-system:FedoraObject-3.0>)
    from <#ri>
    where $a $b $c
